     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W2SHIN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W3SHIN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W4SHIN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W5SHIN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WALOC
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WBKNBN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WCKNBN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WDKNBN
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WEKNBN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
